New Yankee Workshop - 1999 Season Episode 10 - Sink Base

Episode # 9910.  This episode is no longer for sale and has been discontinued on the New Yankee Workshop website.  So I guess it is now obsolete.  However, as usual, Norm produces one good show.  It is in avi format, from a british source. If you like it, be sure to buy other tapes/dvd/plans from newyankee.com
